268
00:20:42,410 --> 00:20:48,410
If we keep allocating money to every ministry's needs,

269
00:20:48,410 --> 00:20:51,150
we're going to create a bigger problem.

270
00:20:52,170 --> 00:20:56,800
This problem must be dealt with at its roots.

271
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:59,590
Are you talking about getting rid of corruption?

272
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:01,000
That's right.

273
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:06,310
The treasury's money has gone to corrupt officials.

274
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:08,310
It's no use, no matter how much money you allocate.

275
00:21:08,310 --> 00:21:12,410
In the end, it's the problem of the law.

276
00:21:12,410 --> 00:21:14,960
A heavy punishment is needed

277
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:17,140
to get rid of corruption.

278
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:23,910
But won't doing this bring the opposite effect?

279
00:21:25,540 --> 00:21:28,320
Zang Hai.

280
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:34,110
If you can think of that,

281
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:40,190
it's very good.

282
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:43,640
This is also what I'm most worried about.

283
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:46,400
The corruption culture in the imperial court

284
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:48,400
happens mostly due to officials

285
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:52,270
who can't feed their families with their meager salaries.

286
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:56,340
If you don't want them to harm the common people,

287
00:21:56,340 --> 00:21:59,530
killing a few of them won't solve the problem.

288
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:03,690
I've petitioned the Emperor

289
00:22:03,690 --> 00:22:08,670
to increase the salaries of all fifth-rank officials and above by 30%.

290
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:18,860
This is the money that the imperial court must spend.

291
00:22:18,860 --> 00:22:22,250
One must have a roof above their head and a full stomach.

292
00:22:22,250 --> 00:22:24,240
Officials must be able to feed their families

293
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:27,030
so they don't prey on the people.

294
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:29,490
This is a good method indeed.

295
00:22:30,250 --> 00:22:31,970
However...

296
00:22:31,970 --> 00:22:35,300
shouldn't we start from those working closely with the people?

297
00:22:35,300 --> 00:22:38,100
If the treasury has a lot of money,

298
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:40,620
I will surely do that.

299
00:22:40,620 --> 00:22:47,090
However, prioritizing the small officials over the powerful officials...

300
00:22:48,550 --> 00:22:51,810
is not something even the Emperor can do.

301
00:22:56,030 --> 00:23:00,310
As the saying goes, "If one intends to take something,

302
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:02,770
one must first give something away."

303
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:08,070
You are involved in the imperial court now.

304
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:12,400
You must remember this in the future.

305
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,680
Yes.

306
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:15,490
I will remember it.

307
00:23:21,350 --> 00:23:24,890
Tong'er came today and recognized the painting to be Official Zhao's.

308
00:23:24,890 --> 00:23:27,480
She even asked how the painting ended up in our place.

309
00:23:31,450 --> 00:23:33,070
It's his indeed.

310
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:36,760
This is very suspicious indeed.

311
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:42,900
I've never lied to Tong'er before.

312
00:23:42,900 --> 00:23:44,970
I didn't tell her the truth today

313
00:23:44,970 --> 00:23:46,730
and I feel a little guilty.

314
00:23:46,730 --> 00:23:49,580
She is my best friend.

315
00:23:49,580 --> 00:23:52,510
I really hope Official Zhao is just your benefactor

316
00:23:52,510 --> 00:23:54,530
and not your enemy.

317
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:14,980
Tong'er.

318
00:24:15,890 --> 00:24:17,390
Father.

319
00:24:18,490 --> 00:24:20,830
What are you looking for?

320
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:25,490
Father, did you give Shi Yiping this painting?

321
00:24:26,540 --> 00:24:28,550
Which painting?

322
00:24:28,550 --> 00:24:32,790
The "Landscape of Mount Yuren" painting that was kept here previously.

323
00:24:33,510 --> 00:24:35,370
That painting?

324
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:42,140
Previously, I went to visit the Shi residence with my colleagues

325
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:46,100
for a so-called painting and calligraphy appreciation session.

326
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:49,140
I brought this painting with me without much thought.

327
00:24:49,140 --> 00:24:51,860
To my surprise, he loved it.

328
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:54,900
He forced me to give it to him, so I did.

329
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:59,610
I went to hang out with Antu today and saw this painting at her place.

330
00:24:59,610 --> 00:25:01,650
I thought I was mistaken

331
00:25:01,650 --> 00:25:05,520
but when I came back and looked for it, the painting was indeed yours.

332
00:25:06,780 --> 00:25:09,900
This painting should belong to the imperial court

333
00:25:09,900 --> 00:25:15,490
now that the Shi Residence was seized following Shi Yiping's death.

334
00:25:15,930 --> 00:25:18,250
How come she possesses the painting?

335
00:25:19,860 --> 00:25:23,970
She said Zang Hai asked the Emperor for it

336
00:25:23,970 --> 00:25:28,060
to be given to her as a gift because it was a painting of Dongxia.

337
00:25:30,010 --> 00:25:32,140
I see.

338
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:34,770
Tong'er,

339
00:25:35,450 --> 00:25:37,590
sit with me for a while.

340
00:25:45,450 --> 00:25:48,480
Since your mother passed away,

341
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:52,540
both of us have been relying on each other,

342
00:25:52,540 --> 00:25:54,950
so I allowed you...

343
00:25:56,000 --> 00:26:02,340
to go to Zhen Tower dressed as a man to tell stories.

344
00:26:02,340 --> 00:26:04,190
But now,

345
00:26:05,410 --> 00:26:07,630
you are no longer a child.

346
00:26:08,170 --> 00:26:10,350
It's time to act your age.

347
00:26:10,350 --> 00:26:13,980
But I enjoy reading and telling stories.

348
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:18,000
You've been rebellious

349
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:22,200
since your childhood, because I've always doted on you.

350
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:25,350
You do things without caring about the consequences.

351
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:27,640
You will regret it one day.

352
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:29,410
Father.

353
00:26:29,410 --> 00:26:31,440
Zhen Tower is gone now.

354
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:34,960
You should cease thinking about telling and reading stories anymore.

355
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:40,000
From now on, you should stay home and accompany me more.

356
00:26:42,450 --> 00:26:44,090
Master.

357
00:26:46,970 --> 00:26:49,410
I'm going to work.

358
00:26:49,410 --> 00:26:51,570
Go back and rest.

359
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:15,510
Zhao Geng.

360
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:16,780
Yes, Master.

361
00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:19,390
Tong'er is a lady now.

362
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:23,530
When she goes out in the future,

363
00:27:24,060 --> 00:27:28,320
assign a few men to follow her in case anything happens to her.

364
00:27:28,320 --> 00:27:29,910
Yes.

365
00:27:47,490 --> 00:27:51,010
Official Zang, it's late.

366
00:27:51,010 --> 00:27:52,510
Our work is endless.

367
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:54,130
Continue tomorrow.

368
00:27:54,130 --> 00:27:56,400
I still have work to do for the Ministry of Works

369
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:58,000
and the Imperial Astronomical Bureau tomorrow.

370
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:02,740
Grand Secretary Shi used to reprimand me in the past for being lazy and carefree.

371
00:28:02,740 --> 00:28:07,150
If he were to see you now, he would surely appreciate you.

372
00:28:08,010 --> 00:28:10,150
I'll be going back.

373
00:28:15,510 --> 00:28:16,860
What a pity.

374
00:28:16,860 --> 00:28:18,410
I joined the Cabinet too late.

375
00:28:18,410 --> 00:28:21,450
Otherwise, I could learn from Grand Secretary Shi.

376
00:28:21,450 --> 00:28:24,100
Having a superior who keeps giving me reminders

377
00:28:24,100 --> 00:28:27,870
in political affairs is a lucky thing.

378
00:28:27,870 --> 00:28:32,490
You are different from what I imagined.

379
00:28:34,830 --> 00:28:36,670
What do you mean?

380
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:42,350
Official Zang, you served Zhuang Luyin in the past.

381
00:28:42,350 --> 00:28:44,380
You became an official through recommendation.

382
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:48,450
However, you caused a mess in the imperial court.

383
00:28:48,450 --> 00:28:50,320
In Grand Secretary Shi's opinion,

384
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:54,380
you broke the balance he spent his whole life maintaining.

385
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:56,210
Balance?

386
00:28:56,790 --> 00:29:03,030
But didn't Grand Secretary Shi turn a blind eye to what Cao Jingxian did?

387
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:06,220
Cao Jingxian and Zhuang Luyin

388
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:09,300
were two authoritative figures no one would dare offend.

389
00:29:09,300 --> 00:29:12,540
Grand Secretary Shi had been going against them by leading the Cabinet.

390
00:29:12,540 --> 00:29:14,820
Both of them are dead now.

391
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:19,080
Unfortunately, Grand Secretary Shi passed away as well.

392
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:22,300
However, rumors in the capital are saying

393
00:29:22,300 --> 00:29:25,970
that Grand Secretary Shi was close to Cao Jingxian.

394
00:29:25,970 --> 00:29:30,700
However, he was killed by Cao Jingxian's surveillance officers.

395
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:34,540
They say both of them had a falling out and turned against each other.

396
00:29:34,540 --> 00:29:36,900
Impossible. I don't believe it.

397
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:38,970
Grand Secretary Shi was my superior for many years.

398
00:29:38,970 --> 00:29:41,250
I know him very well.

399
00:29:41,250 --> 00:29:44,330
Official Zang, let me show you something.

400
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,690
This is the name list of Great Yong's officials.

401
00:29:54,690 --> 00:29:56,690
Grand Secretary Shi gave it to me back then.

402
00:29:56,690 --> 00:30:00,940
He started writing this name list when he was the Vice Minister of Personnel.

403
00:30:03,930 --> 00:30:07,170
Everyone said Grand Secretary Shi remembered every official of Great Yong

404
00:30:07,170 --> 00:30:10,550
when he was the Vice Minister of Personnel.

405
00:30:10,550 --> 00:30:14,590
I suppose good memory still has to make way for note-taking.

406
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:17,950
Before the New Year, Grand Secretary Shi saw that I was busy working

407
00:30:17,950 --> 00:30:20,140
and gave me this name list. 
    

408
00:30:20,140 --> 00:30:25,220
The name list has always been kept at the Cabinet, with no one to retrieve it.

409
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:28,838
   

410
00:30:30,510 --> 00:30:31,600
Lu Min?

411
00:30:31,600 --> 00:30:34,078
   

412
00:30:37,250 --> 00:30:39,730
Lu Min...

413
00:30:39,730 --> 00:30:41,900
I noticed this before.

414
00:30:41,900 --> 00:30:45,480
This should be Cao Jingxian's name before he entered the palace.

415
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:48,340
All his foster sons have the surname of "Lu".

416
00:30:48,340 --> 00:30:51,860
He just couldn't give up on passing his lineage.

417
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:10,480
Sir.

418
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:13,750
I didn't know you were coming.

419
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:16,790
Sorry for the poor reception.

420
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:18,480
Sit.

421
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,520
Thank you, sir.

422
00:31:21,270 --> 00:31:23,210
You may leave.

423
00:31:30,410 --> 00:31:32,210
Are you Eunuch Liu?

424
00:31:32,210 --> 00:31:34,760
Yes.

425
00:31:35,590 --> 00:31:41,330
You were the one who taught the new eunuchs the rules in the past.

426
00:31:41,330 --> 00:31:42,830
I want to ask you about someone.

427
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:47,880
If I know something, I will tell you honestly.

428
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,750
Lu Min.

429
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:51,590
Lu Min?

430
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:54,660
Lu Min...

431
00:31:56,650 --> 00:31:57,900
I remember.

432
00:31:57,900 --> 00:31:59,790
Do you really remember?

433
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:01,680
I do.

434
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:06,580
He wasn't castrated when he entered the palace.

435
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:11,930
He had long lost his manhood.

436
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:15,480
He castrated himself.

437
00:32:25,300 --> 00:32:28,070
There are many rules and forms of etiquette in the palace.

438
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:31,140
Those who graduated here

439
00:32:31,140 --> 00:32:34,900
can have a chance of becoming a eunuch at the inner palace.

440
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:39,620
Lu Min was hardworking and liked to study.

441
00:32:39,620 --> 00:32:44,880
It didn't take long for him to learn most of the skills

442
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:48,670
from veterans like us.

443
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:54,060
When it was time for him to change his name and enter the palace,

444
00:32:54,060 --> 00:32:58,970
he was more capable than eunuchs

445
00:32:58,970 --> 00:33:01,380
years his senior.

446
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:04,520
What did he change his name to later?

447
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:07,680
I don't remember.

448
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:14,640
I remember he went to work at the Imperial Stables Directorate.

449
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:18,350
Lu Min was educated, and he could read.

450
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:21,790
He spoke in a formal and elegant way.

451
00:33:21,790 --> 00:33:25,510
He used to say that he shouldn't become a eunuch.

452
00:33:25,510 --> 00:33:27,310
He said if he participated in the exams,

453
00:33:27,310 --> 00:33:29,540
he would surely become a highly-ranked official.

454
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:35,340
He told me he used to study in the best academy in the capital,

455
00:33:35,340 --> 00:33:39,350
the Academy of Great Yong.

456
00:33:49,860 --> 00:33:51,580
Sir,

457
00:33:51,580 --> 00:33:54,110
all the original documents and files

458
00:33:54,110 --> 00:33:59,170
since the establishment of the Academy of Great Yong are stored here.

459
00:33:59,170 --> 00:34:00,340
You may leave.

460
00:34:00,340 --> 00:34:01,880
I can search for it myself.

461
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:03,280
Yes.

462
