463
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:11,911
   

464
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:27,833
   

465
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:35,460
   

466
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:38,066
   

467
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:47,802
   

468
00:36:17,230 --> 00:36:19,190
Master.

469
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:20,590
You're back?

470
00:36:20,590 --> 00:36:21,760
We are having Fried Bean Sauce Noodles tonight.

471
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:24,290
It will take some time.

472
00:36:24,290 --> 00:36:27,190
I'm too tired today and don't have an appetite.

473
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,760
I want to rest for a while.

474
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:32,260
The Cabinet is a difficult place to be.

475
00:36:32,260 --> 00:36:33,670
Look at you.

476
00:36:33,670 --> 00:36:35,050
You hold three positions at once.

477
00:36:35,050 --> 00:36:37,000
There are too many things you need to do.

478
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:38,900
I feel exhausted for you already.

479
00:36:38,900 --> 00:36:43,070
All of these responsibilities are too many

480
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:44,940
and too heavy for me.

481
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:50,250
Why don't I tell Master

482
00:36:50,250 --> 00:36:52,380
and ask him to relieve you of your burden?

483
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:54,110
I'll think about it.

484
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:57,610
Once I think it through, I'll tell him myself.

485
00:36:57,610 --> 00:36:59,340
Xiao Hai.

486
00:37:02,610 --> 00:37:05,800
You're like a stranger to me now.

487
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:09,180
You won't even chat with me.

488
00:37:09,180 --> 00:37:12,610
Have you forgotten about me now that you have Miss Xiang?

489
00:37:14,610 --> 00:37:16,960
When you put it like that,

490
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:20,880
I have no choice but to chat with you.

491
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:24,170
That's more like it.

492
00:37:24,170 --> 00:37:25,790
Peel the garlic.

493
00:37:28,610 --> 00:37:32,570
Master, do you still remember when you asked me

494
00:37:32,570 --> 00:37:36,430
what kind of life I would want to live after getting my revenge?

495
00:37:38,010 --> 00:37:40,410
I couldn't answer you back then.

496
00:37:40,410 --> 00:37:44,940
You also told me the day would come soon.

497
00:37:46,900 --> 00:37:49,380
You were right.

498
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:53,700
I've made my choice

499
00:37:53,700 --> 00:37:57,510
and I'm still an official with my benefactor.

500
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:03,000
But I want to know your answer.

501
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,650
Me?

502
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:10,030
My benefactor asked you to aid me in my revenge.

503
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:11,570
Now that I've taken my revenge,

504
00:38:11,570 --> 00:38:16,000
haven't you thought about what you want to do?

505
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:29,510
Are you calling me useless now?

506
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,960
Since you're in the Cabinet now,

507
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:34,150
you no longer need the things I taught you.

508
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:36,660
That's not what I mean.

509
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:38,660
I know that's not what you mean.

510
00:38:38,660 --> 00:38:41,260
I was just teasing you.

511
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:47,290
Do you really want to know?

512
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:01,840
Royal silver.

513
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:07,190
Master, do you still remember the time when you took me

514
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:09,280
to trick a corrupt official when I was young?

515
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:11,000
I remember.

516
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,510
Look.

517
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:17,380
I have gotten the newly minted royal silver now.

518
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:21,970
Look how much you've achieved.

519
00:39:21,970 --> 00:39:23,670
The royal silver I used back then

520
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:26,260
was the tuition fee I received from your benefactor.

521
00:39:26,260 --> 00:39:29,840
Yet, I spent all of it in the first lesson.

522
00:39:32,220 --> 00:39:35,070
You are good at pretending to be an official.

523
00:39:35,070 --> 00:39:38,270
Did you learn it from my benefactor?

524
00:39:38,270 --> 00:39:42,030
Why don't you become an official?

525
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:43,880
That won't do.

526
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:46,510
I'm just a fraud.

527
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:49,340
I'll be exposed if I become an official.

528
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:55,360
I don't think so.

529
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:06,710
We humans don't need to live for a certain goal.

530
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:10,360
Living our days with people we care about by our side,

531
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,000
doesn't it sound good?

532
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:15,130
You are in the capital, and your benefactor is also in the capital.

533
00:40:15,130 --> 00:40:17,130
Where else can I go?

534
00:40:17,130 --> 00:40:21,550
I'll just serve you and become a cook.

535
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:23,880
If I can't teach you anything else,

536
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:26,790
I'll feed you instead.

537
